Explosion in Russian North Caucasus Region Kills 8, Injures 6

-- B y   L y u b o v   P r o n i n a
-- 
2011-09-28T17:59:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-28/explosion-in-russian-north-caucasus-region-kills-8-injures-6.html
A car exploded today in the
Dagestan region in  Russia ’s North Caucasus, killing a police
officer and seven civilians including an 11-year-old girl, the
Investigative Committee said.  Six police officers were hospitalized with wounds,
according to a statement on the committee’s website.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lyubov Pronina in Moscow at 
 lpronina@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
